---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessible IoT">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Accessible IoT</h1>

    <div class="badge">
      Towards Accessibility Assessment Toolkits for the Internet of Things
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>This page is an effort to provide accessibility assessment tools to the Internet of Things.</p>
      <p>Our first effort is to work on an accessibility assessment Toolkits for Inclusive IoT Design using Onbody Sensing.</p>
      <p>We propose to build Open Accessibility Assessment Toolkits for Inclusive IoT Design that will provide a foundation for evaluating diverse IoT services in terms of user-perceived accessibility first using on-body sensing. We provide the first steps to an Inclusive IoT architecture enabling an in-situ, dynamic system reconfiguration based on the user's implicit feedback.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>JST Presto Grant</h2>
      <p><strong>Grant Number:</strong> JPMJPR2132</p>
      <p><strong>Period:</strong> 2021-2025</p>
      <p><strong>Principal Investigator:</strong> Kai Kunze</p>
      <p>This website showcases the research outputs and achievements from our JST Presto grant focusing on accessibility assessment tools for the Internet of Things.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Quick Stats</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>19+ Publications (2021-2025)</li>
        <li>7 Research Themes</li>
        <li>Top-tier venues: CHI, UbiComp, UIST, ETRA</li>
        <li>Focus: Accessibility, Inclusive Design, IoT</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
